title: Classic Frames + Actions (with serials)
description:
This is the first 6 sets of classic frames from www.humansoftware.com

There are hundres of different types of frames; portrait, landscape and oval.

These frames work on Photoshop 7, CS, CS2 and CS3, i know i&#039;ve tried them on all these photoshops.

I have also been informed that they work with Paint Shop Pro, but i cannot confirm this, as i&#039;ve never used PSP.

In case these aren&#039;t enough for you, I&#039;ve also included approx 345 Photoshop Actions, made by various people (not mine alas).

All in all, a great bundle for any serious photoshop user, if anyone has other sets of these frames, would appreciate a copy.  I&#039;ve also included serial number, if you install all six, one serial number activates them all (or as many as you install).  Magic Frames has a seperate number, don&#039;t mix them up.  Magic frames has approx 2,000 different frames.  

Hope you enjoy these as much as i do.
